WEBVTT

00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:01.159
Most of them were killed

00:01:01.159 --> 00:01:02.932
either in the early days of the war

00:01:02.932 --> 00:01:04.298
or towards the end of the hostilities,

00:01:04.298 --> 00:01:07.477
when U.N. safe zones like Srebrenica

00:01:07.477 --> 00:01:10.522
fell into the hands of the Serb army.

00:01:10.522 --> 00:01:12.640
The international criminal tribunal

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:14.330
delivered a number of sentences

00:01:14.330 --> 00:01:17.109
for crimes against humanity and genocide.

00:01:17.109 --> 00:01:20.618
Genocide is a systematic and deliberate

00:01:20.618 --> 00:01:24.288
destruction of a racial, political, religious

00:01:24.288 --> 00:01:25.960
or ethnic group.

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:28.540
As much as genocide is about killing.

00:01:28.540 --> 00:01:31.561
It is also about destroying their property,